Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Panama blunder by Reagan
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99nq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 May 1976
Presidential candidate Reagan blunders over Panama Canal policy. Senator Goldwater's influence on Republican votes. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less